[SN]TITLE[SN]
Canadian Grand Prix: Will Lewis Hamilton take sixth Canada pole?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
After the slow-burn of Monaco and engine failures at Indy 500, it's Montreal's turn to lay on the excitement at the Circuit Gilles Villeneuve.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Canada presents a chance for Lewis Hamilton to close the gap on the great Michael Schumacher's record of seven wins there, as the Briton searches for a sixth pole and sixth win.
And add to that the small matter of a 25-point deficit to chip into at the top of the drivers' championship.
